          "front": "what research (or clinical trials) is being done for Neuroleptic Malignant Syndrome ?",
          "back": "The NINDS supports research on neurological disorders such as neuroleptic malignant syndrome. Much of this research focuses on finding ways to prevent and treat the disorder."
